WEBVTT

00:59.480 --> 01:00.740
Xiaocen, you're here.

01:01.200 --> 01:03.120
I heard you were sick a few days ago.

01:03.120 --> 01:04.650
Are you feeling better now?

01:04.920 --> 01:05.650
Much better.

01:07.160 --> 01:08.480
These past few days you weren't here,

01:08.480 --> 01:10.480
I felt Xu Xiao wasn't in a good state.

01:10.760 --> 01:12.620
He seemed very worried about you.

01:21.160 --> 01:22.020
Xu Xiao is here.

01:22.360 --> 01:23.220
Xu Xiao is here.

01:31.200 --> 01:31.720
Are you

01:33.160 --> 01:34.090
feeling better?

01:35.240 --> 01:35.970
I'm fine now.

01:38.560 --> 01:40.890
My mom didn't say anything to you, did she?

01:43.000 --> 01:43.800
Nothing much.

01:49.400 --> 01:49.930
Morning.

01:58.680 --> 01:59.810
Are you alright now?

02:01.200 --> 02:02.060
Class monitor,

02:02.240 --> 02:03.640
is everyone here?

02:04.040 --> 02:04.960
Everyone's here.

02:04.960 --> 02:05.480
Class,

02:06.200 --> 02:08.039
Today is the last class of Introduction to Cultural Relics Studies

02:08.039 --> 02:09.560
for this semester.

02:10.120 --> 02:11.180
Time really flies.

02:11.600 --> 02:13.360
The semester has gone by in a flash.

02:13.360 --> 02:14.880
I wonder if you still remember

02:14.880 --> 02:17.120
how you felt when you first walked into this classroom

02:17.120 --> 02:18.720
and sat in these seats.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.120
Xiaocen.

02:24.400 --> 02:25.160
Mr. Yue.

02:25.920 --> 02:26.520
Xiaocen,

02:28.240 --> 02:29.500
where's your partner?

02:31.320 --> 02:32.450
Probably behind me.

02:43.079 --> 02:43.800
Hurry up.

02:44.360 --> 02:44.960
What's wrong?

02:44.960 --> 02:46.400
Did you hear

02:46.640 --> 02:48.120
about your little partner?

02:48.120 --> 02:48.800
Hear what?

02:50.400 --> 02:52.520
Her mother called the department

02:52.520 --> 02:54.200
asking about changing her major.

02:54.200 --> 02:55.000
I didn't know.

02:57.079 --> 02:59.140
What are you waiting for? Go quickly.

03:02.520 --> 03:03.480
These parents

03:04.200 --> 03:06.360
are more troublesome than the students.

03:06.360 --> 03:07.160
Zhao Xiaocen!

03:07.320 --> 03:08.120
Zhao Xiaocen!

03:14.320 --> 03:15.980
You want to change your major.

03:17.120 --> 03:17.800
I'm sorry.

03:19.120 --> 03:19.520
I

03:20.040 --> 03:21.640
didn't know how to tell you.

03:21.840 --> 03:23.040
I've told you before.

03:23.600 --> 03:24.400
In this world,

03:24.400 --> 03:26.860
I'm the last person you need to apologize to.

03:30.480 --> 03:31.740
I just want to tell you,

03:33.920 --> 03:36.050
you need to think more about yourself.

03:37.040 --> 03:38.300
Follow your own heart.

03:40.760 --> 03:42.220
No matter what you choose,

03:44.079 --> 03:44.880
I will respect

03:46.720 --> 03:47.650
and support you.

04:10.360 --> 04:11.840
Your dad and I have discussed it.

04:11.840 --> 04:12.560
We're changing your major.

04:12.560 --> 04:13.960
We've made the decision.

04:14.000 --> 04:15.960
Then what exactly are you discussing with me?

04:15.960 --> 04:16.920
I am your mother.

04:17.320 --> 04:18.839
You have to do as I say.

04:21.079 --> 04:23.410
Haven't you ever thought about going out?

04:24.000 --> 04:24.600
Of course.

04:25.400 --> 04:26.320
I've always wanted to go

04:26.320 --> 04:27.920
to the place where you grew up

04:28.160 --> 04:29.020
and take a look.

04:38.920 --> 04:40.000
I want to be like you

04:41.400 --> 04:42.600
and be brave for once.

04:44.520 --> 04:45.080
Xiaocen.

04:48.240 --> 04:48.920
I like you.

05:39.880 --> 05:43.080
Don't keep looking at me like that, okay?

05:43.360 --> 05:45.200
It's like I'm about to die.

05:46.200 --> 05:48.200
I'm just worried about you, Master.

05:50.760 --> 05:51.920
How is the kiln?

05:52.720 --> 05:54.120
The fire is out and it's cooling.

05:54.120 --> 05:55.250
Everything is fine.

05:56.120 --> 05:56.680
Good.

05:58.360 --> 06:00.400
Crank it up a bit for me.

06:05.880 --> 06:07.080
Is this okay, Master?

06:07.080 --> 06:07.810
A bit higher.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.120
Good, good.

06:13.160 --> 06:14.120
Guan Lin.

06:17.200 --> 06:18.080
You know,

06:18.560 --> 06:20.520
when firing a wood kiln,

06:21.600 --> 06:23.330
there are eight leg positions.

06:23.560 --> 06:24.840
Eight levels.

06:25.560 --> 06:26.920
The top three are

06:28.600 --> 06:31.040
top stacker,

06:31.880 --> 06:33.240
kiln planner,

06:34.080 --> 06:35.200
and chief kiln.

06:37.760 --> 06:39.360
The bottom three are...

06:39.440 --> 06:40.080
I know.

06:41.120 --> 06:43.440
Don't interrupt. Let me finish.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.440
The bottom three are

06:47.000 --> 06:50.600
First Apprentice, Second Apprentice, and Third Apprentice.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.280
In the middle,

06:52.600 --> 06:53.159
there are

06:53.520 --> 06:56.240
young potter and bottom stacker.

06:57.800 --> 07:01.840
I started from the lowest level, First Apprentice.

07:02.960 --> 07:04.480
Every day,

07:05.560 --> 07:08.680
I spent 16 or 17 hours in the kiln.

07:10.120 --> 07:11.480
Every three days,

07:11.840 --> 07:13.100
we fired the kiln once.

07:14.360 --> 07:15.720
So every year,

07:18.440 --> 07:21.160
I had to practice in front of the kiln

07:21.920 --> 07:24.280
more than a hundred times a year.

07:25.680 --> 07:26.880
Let's talk about this

07:26.960 --> 07:28.200
when we get back.

07:28.680 --> 07:29.610
Have some water.

07:30.080 --> 07:30.440
Here.

07:42.200 --> 07:42.960
Guan Lin.

07:43.920 --> 07:45.920
You've been with me for these years,

07:46.480 --> 07:47.600
and I've only taught you

07:47.600 --> 07:49.600
this one skill.

07:53.159 --> 07:55.680
Don't complain it's too slow.

07:59.440 --> 08:00.320
Guan Lin.

08:01.760 --> 08:03.680
You need to know that firing a kiln

08:06.120 --> 08:07.480
is a lifelong pursuit.

08:09.200 --> 08:10.160
Master.

08:10.720 --> 08:11.920
I was wrong.

08:11.960 --> 08:12.320
I was

08:12.840 --> 08:13.960
too slow to realize.

08:13.960 --> 08:15.760
You should have told me this earlier.

08:15.760 --> 08:16.920
Actually, I was just anxious.

08:16.920 --> 08:18.250
I was worried about you.

08:20.280 --> 08:21.240
Don't cry.

08:21.240 --> 08:22.880
Why are you crying?

08:22.920 --> 08:23.980
No, I'm not crying.

08:25.960 --> 08:30.400
I'm still waiting to see what your first firing of Weijiayao

08:31.440 --> 08:32.760
will produce.

08:33.960 --> 08:35.799
I still want to see you

08:36.600 --> 08:37.880
become a master.

08:38.400 --> 08:40.240
And I'll become a grandmaster.

08:47.840 --> 08:50.560
Why are you wailing like we're in a soap opera?

08:54.800 --> 08:55.600
Students,

08:56.000 --> 08:57.000
time flies.

08:57.800 --> 08:58.560
In a flash,

08:59.080 --> 09:01.140
it's already the end of the semester.

09:01.320 --> 09:04.480
I won't take up too much of your time today.

09:05.080 --> 09:07.680
Xiaocen will collect your papers.

09:08.360 --> 09:09.720
Your final grades

09:10.080 --> 09:12.320
will be based on your papers

09:12.880 --> 09:15.240
and your regular assignments,

09:15.680 --> 09:17.280
which I will grade together.

09:18.200 --> 09:18.840
Students,

09:19.520 --> 09:22.120
you can check them after class.

09:27.880 --> 09:28.560
Xiaocen.

09:30.320 --> 09:32.120
How did you write your thesis?

09:34.760 --> 09:36.040
I wrote that

09:37.200 --> 09:38.530
porcelain restoration

09:38.760 --> 09:41.490
is actually a modern inheritance of ancient art.

09:41.960 --> 09:44.120
Inheritance means

09:44.760 --> 09:46.560
passing down the fundamentals,

09:47.080 --> 09:49.480
while adapting to current needs.

09:50.680 --> 09:52.920
Only by combining these two

09:53.400 --> 09:54.930
can it be true inheritance.

09:55.800 --> 09:58.360
This is also what I experienced

09:58.360 --> 09:59.960
and realized this semester.

10:01.520 --> 10:02.160
Xiaocen.

10:04.720 --> 10:06.760
You have a feel for art,

10:06.760 --> 10:08.920
and you are thoughtful and calm.

10:09.320 --> 10:11.840
These traits make you highly suited for

10:11.880 --> 10:13.610
cultural relics restoration.

10:14.400 --> 10:14.960
But,

10:16.560 --> 10:17.720
I heard your mother

10:18.680 --> 10:21.010
is arranging for you to change your major.

10:21.680 --> 10:22.720
What do you think?

10:27.560 --> 10:30.160
I think my family's opinion

10:30.160 --> 10:31.320
is quite important.

10:32.280 --> 10:33.880
I want to hear your opinion,

10:34.560 --> 10:35.640
your own thoughts.

10:38.040 --> 10:38.480
I...

10:39.000 --> 10:42.400
I seem to have always listened to my mother since I was little.

10:42.640 --> 10:43.360
Xiaocen.

10:44.080 --> 10:45.280
The first encounter.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.960
It all stems from fate.

10:49.760 --> 10:51.560
Only your own love

10:52.520 --> 10:54.760
can offset the long years.

10:57.920 --> 10:58.520
Of course,

10:58.800 --> 10:59.200
this

10:59.480 --> 11:02.000
also includes the people

11:02.880 --> 11:04.080
and things around us.

11:06.240 --> 11:07.240
Think about it.

11:09.520 --> 11:10.580
It's the holidays.

11:10.600 --> 11:12.600
I will read the paper when I get back.

11:12.800 --> 11:15.040
Think of your own answer.

11:16.520 --> 11:18.520
I believe you will find the answer.

11:19.200 --> 11:20.130
Happy holidays.

11:47.640 --> 11:48.700
It's so beautiful.

11:55.080 --> 11:56.200
The delicate shape

11:56.680 --> 11:57.680
and gentle luster

11:58.000 --> 11:59.930
complement each other perfectly.

12:03.080 --> 12:03.680
Master.

12:04.120 --> 12:04.800
Mr. Wei.

12:05.280 --> 12:05.920
It's done.

12:11.000 --> 12:11.400
Great.

12:11.480 --> 12:13.080
Congratulations, Mr. Guan.

12:13.080 --> 12:13.720
Next time,

12:14.000 --> 12:15.080
we must work with you again.

12:15.080 --> 12:15.640
Okay.

12:16.680 --> 12:17.210
Mr. Guan,

12:17.240 --> 12:18.640
can I take a photo with you?

12:18.640 --> 12:19.560
Sure. Come.

12:20.800 --> 12:21.280
Wait.

12:23.600 --> 12:24.320
Guan Lin.

12:26.320 --> 12:27.320
Come, sit here.

12:28.000 --> 12:28.960
It's inappropriate, Master.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.090
You should sit here.

12:31.760 --> 12:32.720
Sit down.

12:32.800 --> 12:33.200
No.

12:33.240 --> 12:34.040
Have a seat, Mr. Guan.

12:34.040 --> 12:34.840
Have a seat, Guan Lin.

12:34.840 --> 12:35.560
Sit down.

12:35.560 --> 12:36.080
Master, I...

12:36.080 --> 12:37.080
Take the picture.

12:39.400 --> 12:39.880
Please.

12:40.120 --> 12:41.720
Master, maybe you should...

12:41.800 --> 12:43.800
Don't look at me. Look at the camera.

12:44.680 --> 12:45.160
Three.

12:45.520 --> 12:46.000
Two.

12:46.480 --> 12:46.880
One.

12:47.320 --> 12:47.760
Smile.

13:11.840 --> 13:12.400
Sister,

13:13.480 --> 13:16.240
Xiaocen hasn't been eating well lately.

13:19.040 --> 13:19.900
It's a process.

13:20.640 --> 13:22.240
It'll be fine once it passes.

13:28.280 --> 13:29.320
As for her,

13:29.680 --> 13:31.340
she seems fine during the day.

13:32.640 --> 13:34.960
But at night, she often

13:35.120 --> 13:36.450
cries alone in her room.

13:37.600 --> 13:40.240
Sometimes I see her staring out the window.

13:43.280 --> 13:45.160
Xiaocen is already weak.

13:46.280 --> 13:48.680
She looks like the wind could blow her over.

13:49.240 --> 13:50.840
She's feeling so miserable,

13:51.360 --> 13:52.620
yet she won't tell you.

13:53.640 --> 13:55.200
It breaks my heart to see.

13:55.400 --> 13:57.000
It's because I care about her

13:57.040 --> 13:58.320
that I'm afraid she'll be wronged,

13:58.320 --> 14:00.180
with nowhere to cry in the future.

14:01.040 --> 14:02.680
Knowing it's impossible,

14:03.320 --> 14:04.720
why should I support her?

14:05.480 --> 14:07.480
Why are you so sure it won't work out?

14:08.920 --> 14:10.380
Let's make an assumption.

14:10.600 --> 14:11.720
I mean, what if.

14:13.560 --> 14:15.690
What if they actually end up together?

14:18.760 --> 14:20.720
Can't Xiaocen stay in Jingdezhen?

14:26.840 --> 14:29.280
It'd be good for her career here.

14:29.600 --> 14:30.600
Plus, I'm here too.

14:30.600 --> 14:31.680
I can help her.

14:34.720 --> 14:36.520
What if she stays in Jingdezhen?

14:39.680 --> 14:40.480
What if?

14:50.760 --> 14:52.620
What if she ends up like me? Right?

15:00.480 --> 15:01.160
Qingfang,

15:02.120 --> 15:04.200
can you stop dwelling on the past?

15:10.400 --> 15:11.080
If I don't,

15:12.240 --> 15:14.100
does that mean it never happened?

15:16.640 --> 15:17.400
Back then,

15:17.720 --> 15:19.780
you married and moved here all alone.

15:20.640 --> 15:21.570
Do you remember?

15:22.480 --> 15:24.210
You used to call me all the time.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.720
Qingfang,

15:26.360 --> 15:27.960
I'm not used to the food here.

15:27.960 --> 15:29.560
I can't adapt to the climate.

15:30.200 --> 15:31.080
And that man,

15:31.800 --> 15:33.060
didn't treat you well.

15:36.160 --> 15:36.960
Later,

15:38.200 --> 15:40.000
you raised Xing all by yourself.

15:40.720 --> 15:42.380
How did you get through it all?

15:43.520 --> 15:44.800
As your older sister,

15:45.800 --> 15:47.060
don't you think I know?

16:13.320 --> 16:13.880
Come in.

16:16.200 --> 16:16.720
Mom.

16:17.240 --> 16:17.840
Xiaocen.

16:18.120 --> 16:18.920
Well,

16:19.280 --> 16:21.800
you can pack up some things first

16:21.880 --> 16:22.680
and mail them.

16:22.720 --> 16:23.400
Got it.

16:24.560 --> 16:25.240
By the way,

16:25.480 --> 16:27.280
can you check your grades today?

16:30.240 --> 16:30.920
Okay.

16:31.400 --> 16:33.200
Take your time packing. No rush.

16:33.720 --> 16:34.920
I'll get back to work.

17:02.280 --> 17:03.720
Xu, what are you doing?

17:05.920 --> 17:06.920
Checking scores.

17:08.400 --> 17:09.400
Checking yours

17:09.400 --> 17:10.560
or Xiaocen's?

17:13.560 --> 17:14.920
You don't even know your own score,

17:14.920 --> 17:16.720
yet you're checking Xiaocen's?

17:18.000 --> 17:18.720
Okay, I won't ask.

17:18.720 --> 17:19.520
Just tell me,

17:19.520 --> 17:20.319
how did she do?

17:22.319 --> 17:23.079
Top five.

17:23.079 --> 17:23.800
Not bad!

17:23.880 --> 17:25.000
Such a big improvement.

17:25.000 --> 17:25.880
It must be you

17:25.880 --> 17:27.079
who tutored her well.

17:30.720 --> 17:32.240
Why don't you take the chance to call her?

17:32.240 --> 17:33.120
What are you waiting for?

17:33.120 --> 17:34.250
If you don't, I will.

17:34.800 --> 17:36.200
What's the number again?

17:37.800 --> 17:38.680
Just kidding.

17:38.880 --> 17:39.610
Call her now.

17:53.840 --> 17:54.600
Xiaocen.

17:55.360 --> 17:56.490
Initial encounters

17:57.360 --> 17:59.200
all stem from fate.

18:00.480 --> 18:02.200
Only your own passion

18:02.560 --> 18:04.880
can offset the long years.

18:05.280 --> 18:06.920
What exactly do I want?

18:16.200 --> 18:18.240
What exactly do I really want?

18:26.960 --> 18:27.480
Sister.

18:27.800 --> 18:29.680
These are some fruits for Xiaocen

18:29.720 --> 18:30.780
to eat on the plane.

18:31.560 --> 18:32.560
Oh, right. And...

18:34.040 --> 18:36.160
This is Jingdezhen porcelain for Brother-in-Law.

18:36.160 --> 18:37.320
There's also Fuliang tea inside.

18:37.320 --> 18:38.520
Okay, stop bringing things.

18:38.520 --> 18:39.720
It won't fit anymore.

18:40.320 --> 18:41.800
Isn't Brother-in-Law picking you up?

18:41.800 --> 18:42.930
You won't get tired.

18:44.720 --> 18:46.600
Cencen, get ready to go.

18:55.800 --> 18:56.280
Sister.

18:56.680 --> 18:58.920
Say hi to my brother-in-law for me when you get home.

18:58.920 --> 18:59.360
Okay.

19:00.480 --> 19:01.340
Let me tell you.

19:01.400 --> 19:02.880
You still need to discipline Xiaoxing,

19:02.880 --> 19:04.480
especially since he's a boy.

19:04.520 --> 19:05.720
You have to be strict

19:05.720 --> 19:06.720
and keep a close eye on him.

19:06.720 --> 19:07.560
Otherwise,

19:07.600 --> 19:08.400
he'll really get out of hand.

19:08.400 --> 19:08.960
Did you hear me?

19:08.960 --> 19:10.160
Don't worry, Sister.

19:10.520 --> 19:11.480
I got it.

19:11.720 --> 19:13.600
Remember to call me when you get home.

19:13.600 --> 19:15.730
You should think more about yourself.

19:15.800 --> 19:16.920
Follow your heart.

19:17.360 --> 19:19.090
No matter what choice you make,

19:19.760 --> 19:20.560
I will respect

19:22.200 --> 19:23.130
and support you.

19:24.720 --> 19:25.800
Xiaocen, hurry up.

19:27.520 --> 19:28.580
Mom, I'm not going.

19:33.240 --> 19:34.170
What did you say?

19:35.800 --> 19:36.200
I...

19:36.600 --> 19:37.860
I said I'm not leaving.

19:40.480 --> 19:41.840
No, what do you mean?

19:42.200 --> 19:43.200
Aren't you going back to

19:43.200 --> 19:45.130
keep your dad company this summer?

19:45.720 --> 19:47.040
I already told Dad.

19:47.640 --> 19:49.970
I'm staying at my aunt's for the holidays.

19:52.240 --> 19:53.680
What I want to tell you is,

19:56.360 --> 19:58.360
I'm not leaving afterwards either.

20:00.520 --> 20:02.580
What nonsense are you talking about?

20:04.080 --> 20:06.120
Go through security with me right now.

20:06.120 --> 20:07.520
We can talk when we get home.

20:07.520 --> 20:09.650
I need to make it clear to you right now.

20:10.120 --> 20:11.480
I'm not leaving today.

20:13.840 --> 20:15.120
Did that guy named Xu Xiao

20:15.120 --> 20:16.880
tell you a bunch of nonsense?

20:16.880 --> 20:17.440
No.

20:18.800 --> 20:20.260
These are my own thoughts.

20:23.320 --> 20:23.800
Mom.

20:24.720 --> 20:26.600
I'm 19 years old now.

20:27.720 --> 20:29.850
I have the right to make my own choices.

20:31.560 --> 20:33.920
I've always listened to you since I was little.

20:33.920 --> 20:34.720
You said

20:35.360 --> 20:37.560
eating too much sugar is bad for health,

20:38.720 --> 20:40.080
so I barely ate any.

20:41.480 --> 20:43.940
You said girls shouldn't dress too flashily

20:44.000 --> 20:45.360
or wear heavy makeup.

20:45.520 --> 20:47.080
You also said Chinese medicine should be drunk in one gulp.

20:47.080 --> 20:48.340
I listened to all of it.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.040
Because I know you mean well.

20:52.840 --> 20:54.320
But gradually, I can't tell

20:54.320 --> 20:55.240
which are your thoughts

20:55.240 --> 20:56.560
and which are my own.

20:58.720 --> 20:59.240
Mom.

21:00.280 --> 21:03.010
You were the one who told me to come to Jingdezhen.

21:03.080 --> 21:05.810
You made me choose cultural relics restoration.

21:07.560 --> 21:09.280
Before I came here, I didn't know

21:09.280 --> 21:10.610
what I would go through.

21:12.680 --> 21:13.880
But I found that

21:14.840 --> 21:16.600
I fell in love with porcelain

21:23.280 --> 21:24.680
and cultural relics.

21:32.040 --> 21:33.770
I fell in love with Jingdezhen.

21:45.960 --> 21:47.420
I fell in love with Xu Xiao.

21:52.880 --> 21:53.720
I found that

21:53.720 --> 21:55.040
when I do things,

21:55.040 --> 21:56.480
I can have emotions.

21:57.640 --> 21:58.680
I can be happy,

21:58.680 --> 21:59.360
cheerful,

21:59.360 --> 22:01.560
and find it hard to let go of some things.

22:04.040 --> 22:05.640
I don't have to listen to you.

22:11.560 --> 22:13.480
I fell in love with cultural relics restoration.

22:13.480 --> 22:16.540
Four years of college is not enough for me to explore it.

22:16.840 --> 22:17.840
I want to stay here

22:18.560 --> 22:21.220
and spend my whole life exploring and learning.

22:23.120 --> 22:24.050
Your whole life?

22:25.600 --> 22:26.880
How old are you now

22:27.640 --> 22:29.640
to be talking about your whole life?

22:30.240 --> 22:30.920
All I know is

22:30.920 --> 22:33.780
that this is the first time I have a clear direction.

22:34.040 --> 22:36.040
Nothing you say will change my mind.

22:39.600 --> 22:40.320
Right now,

22:40.920 --> 22:42.960
I don't want to discuss this with you anymore.

22:42.960 --> 22:44.120
Right now, immediately,

22:44.120 --> 22:45.850
come through security with me.

22:47.320 --> 22:47.880
Aunt.

22:49.240 --> 22:50.500
I'll go to your car now.

22:53.600 --> 22:54.400
Zhao Xiaocen!

22:55.600 --> 22:56.400
Zhao Xiaocen!

22:57.920 --> 22:59.580
The car is unlocked, Xiaocen!

23:25.400 --> 23:26.000
Qingfang.

23:27.040 --> 23:28.170
Since we were young,

23:28.840 --> 23:29.920
you were 90% right

23:30.400 --> 23:31.920
about everything.

23:33.280 --> 23:34.560
But today,

23:34.840 --> 23:36.900
I don't think you did the right thing.

23:38.520 --> 23:40.600
Did you hear what Xiaocen just said?

23:42.280 --> 23:43.360
For all these years,

23:43.360 --> 23:44.360
this is the first time

23:44.360 --> 23:45.400
I've seen her so determined

23:45.400 --> 23:46.720
to do something.

23:51.600 --> 23:52.120
Yes.

23:54.040 --> 23:56.370
Looking at the way she spoke to me just now,

23:57.720 --> 24:00.120
I almost didn't recognize my own daughter.

24:02.240 --> 24:04.400
Look whose daughter she is.

24:08.040 --> 24:09.720
I'm just afraid she'll regret it later,

24:09.720 --> 24:10.680
you know?

24:11.160 --> 24:13.220
You always say we'll regret it later.

24:14.720 --> 24:15.720
But you know what?

24:16.480 --> 24:17.610
For all these years,

24:17.840 --> 24:18.840
there's something

24:18.840 --> 24:20.320
I never dared to tell you.

24:24.120 --> 24:25.580
I have never regretted it.

24:27.360 --> 24:29.120
You can say I chose the wrong man,

24:29.120 --> 24:31.320
but I have never regretted coming here.

24:32.840 --> 24:34.640
If I hadn't come to Jingdezhen,

24:35.200 --> 24:36.930
I wouldn't have my current life

24:37.480 --> 24:38.400
and career,

24:39.200 --> 24:40.600
let alone Xing.

24:41.720 --> 24:43.120
I love everything here.

24:47.880 --> 24:48.480
Qingfang,

24:49.600 --> 24:51.460
give yourself a little more time,

24:51.800 --> 24:53.840
and you will fall in love with this place

24:53.840 --> 24:55.240
just like Xiaocen and me.

25:39.160 --> 25:39.920
Mom.

25:41.640 --> 25:42.160
Sister.

25:43.560 --> 25:44.040
Sister.

25:54.000 --> 25:54.640
Mom.

26:09.280 --> 26:10.200
Cencen.

26:11.840 --> 26:12.400
Cencen.

26:24.920 --> 26:26.960
Let's all calm down for a bit.

26:29.920 --> 26:31.120
I'll head back first.

26:37.280 --> 26:38.040
It seems

26:39.080 --> 26:40.720
I really should accept

26:41.720 --> 26:43.120
that you've grown up.

26:46.960 --> 26:47.690
Stop crying.

26:52.120 --> 26:53.240
Thank you, Mom.

26:53.240 --> 26:53.680
Don't cry.
